data.name: SqlSelectCommand1.CommandText
data.value: SELECT Program, DrawingNumber, DrawingTitle, Location, ADCN, DCN, DrawingType, DwgRevision, DwgRequestBy, DwgRequestDate, Releaser, Status, ActualFinishDate, Notes, RecordID, AIM, DocumentType FROM tblDrawings

data.name: SqlInsertCommand1.CommandText
data.value: INSERT INTO [tblDrawings] ([Program], [DrawingNumber], [DrawingTitle], [Location], [ADCN], [DCN], [DrawingType], [DwgRevision], [DwgRequestBy], [DwgRequestDate], [Releaser], [Status], [ActualFinishDate], [Notes], [AIM], [DocumentType]) VALUES (@Program, @DrawingNumber, @DrawingTitle, @Location, @ADCN, @DCN, @DrawingType, @DwgRevision, @DwgRequestBy, @DwgRequestDate, @Releaser, @Status, @ActualFinishDate, @Notes, @AIM, @DocumentType); SELECT Program, DrawingNumber, DrawingTitle, Location, ADCN, DCN, DrawingType, DwgRevision, DwgRequestBy, DwgRequestDate, Releaser, Status, ActualFinishDate, Notes, RecordID, AIM, DocumentType FROM tblDrawings WHERE (RecordID = SCOPE_IDENTITY())

data.name: SqlUpdateCommand1.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE [tblDrawings] SET [Program] = @Program, [DrawingNumber] = @DrawingNumber, [DrawingTitle] = @DrawingTitle, [Location] = @Location, [ADCN] = @ADCN, [DCN] = @DCN, [DrawingType] = @DrawingType, [DwgRevision] = @DwgRevision, [DwgRequestBy] = @DwgRequestBy, [DwgRequestDate] = @DwgRequestDate, [Releaser] = @Releaser, [Status] = @Status, [ActualFinishDate] = @ActualFinishDate, [Notes] = @Notes, [AIM] = @AIM, [DocumentType] = @DocumentType WHERE (((@IsNull_Program = 1 AND [Program] IS NULL) OR ([Program] = @Original_Program)) AND ((@IsNull_DrawingNumber = 1 AND [DrawingNumber] IS NULL) OR ([DrawingNumber] = @Original_DrawingNumber)) AND ((@IsNull_DrawingTitle = 1 AND [DrawingTitle] IS NULL) OR ([DrawingTitle] = @Original_DrawingTitle)) AND ((@IsNull_Location = 1 AND [Location] IS NULL) OR ([Location] = @Original_Location)) AND ((@IsNull_ADCN = 1 AND [ADCN] IS NULL) OR ([ADCN] = @Original_ADCN)) AND ((@IsNull_DCN = 1 AND [DCN] IS NULL) OR ([DCN] = @Original_DCN)) AND ((@IsNull_DrawingType = 1 AND [DrawingType] IS NULL) OR ([DrawingType] = @Original_DrawingType)) AND ((@IsNull_DwgRevision = 1 AND [DwgRevision] IS NULL) OR ([DwgRevision] = @Original_DwgRevision)) AND ((@IsNull_DwgRequestBy = 1 AND [DwgRequestBy] IS NULL) OR ([DwgRequestBy] = @Original_DwgRequestBy)) AND ((@IsNull_DwgRequestDate = 1 AND [DwgRequestDate] IS NULL) OR ([DwgRequestDate] = @Original_DwgRequestDate)) AND ((@IsNull_Releaser = 1 AND [Releaser] IS NULL) OR ([Releaser] = @Original_Releaser)) AND ((@IsNull_Status = 1 AND [Status] IS NULL) OR ([Status] = @Original_Status)) AND ((@IsNull_ActualFinishDate = 1 AND [ActualFinishDate] IS NULL) OR ([ActualFinishDate] = @Original_ActualFinishDate)) AND ((@IsNull_Notes = 1 AND [Notes] IS NULL) OR ([Notes] = @Original_Notes)) AND ([RecordID] = @Original_RecordID) AND ((@IsNull_AIM = 1 AND [AIM] IS NULL) OR ([AIM] = @Original_AIM)) AND ((@IsNull_DocumentType = 1 AND [DocumentType] IS NULL) OR ([DocumentType] = @Original_DocumentType))); SELECT Program, DrawingNumber, DrawingTitle, Location, ADCN, DCN, DrawingType, DwgRevision, DwgRequestBy, DwgRequestDate, Releaser, Status, ActualFinishDate, Notes, RecordID, AIM, DocumentType FROM tblDrawings WHERE (RecordID = @RecordID)
